Lohse: 100 habitus 101 median lobe of aedeagus in lateral view 102, 103 median lobe of aedeagus in dorsal view 104 male tergite VIII 105 male sternite VIII 106 female tergite VIII 107 female sternite VIII 108 spermatheca. Scale bars: 1 mm (for habitus); 0.2 mm (remaining).
